IEC 60870-5-104 Client Simulator

Simulate iec104 client/Master,supports all type of ASDU,monitor,command

We can add up to 50 Client node in the simulator. Every Client node will work independently. 
Simulator window shows the Connection status & connection IP Address, port number. 
The user can monitor all data Point information, and quality bits. Send all type of commands, parameter activation, file transfer.

Interoperability:
http://freyrscada.com/docs/FreyrSCADA-IEC-60870-5-104-Client-Interoperability.pdf

